1
00:01:04,916 --> 00:01:08,833
Wilhelmina, Johann asked
me to give you a message.

2
00:01:08,916 --> 00:01:12,625
"Please, my dear friend,
take care of him for us.

3
00:01:12,708 --> 00:01:14,375
His name is Justus."

4
00:01:48,750 --> 00:01:52,250
This child represents
the new way of being

5
00:01:52,333 --> 00:01:54,125
that the God of
Guidance mentioned.

6
00:01:54,208 --> 00:01:56,250
The Heir to Both Worlds.

7
00:01:56,333 --> 00:01:57,708
When Johann realized

8
00:01:57,791 --> 00:01:59,416
that he wouldn't
live much longer,

9
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:01,375
he suddenly had an idea.

10
00:02:03,125 --> 00:02:05,458
There is one way that
we could overcome death.

11
00:02:05,541 --> 00:02:07,208
A child.

12
00:02:07,291 --> 00:02:08,916
A new life, Pheles,

13
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:13,041
one that we can
create together.

14
00:02:13,125 --> 00:02:15,125
Then they knew,

15
00:02:15,208 --> 00:02:16,833
this was the only way

16
00:02:16,916 --> 00:02:19,208
they could continue
to live on together.

17
00:02:19,291 --> 00:02:21,333
They joined both
their beings

18
00:02:21,416 --> 00:02:22,833
to create a new life.

19
00:02:25,166 --> 00:02:27,166
Dear Justus.

20
00:02:27,250 --> 00:02:28,583
Beloved child.

21
00:02:30,375 --> 00:02:31,708
Sweet boy.

22
00:02:31,791 --> 00:02:34,041
Your parents
would be so proud.

23
00:02:50,208 --> 00:02:52,166
Spiral Organ.

24
00:02:52,250 --> 00:02:54,333
Was there sufficient
Power of Existence?

25
00:02:54,416 --> 00:02:55,666
Yes, indeed.

26
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:59,166
There was more than enough
to activate the spell.

27
00:02:59,250 --> 00:03:00,583
My work is done.

28
00:03:00,666 --> 00:03:02,125
Now I understand.

29
00:03:02,208 --> 00:03:04,958
The remaining Power of
Existence was your reward.

30
00:03:05,041 --> 00:03:06,750
What'll you do with it?

31
00:03:06,833 --> 00:03:17,333
Restore something special
that was once beyond repair.

32
00:03:21,375 --> 00:03:22,708
Thanks a lot.

33
00:03:22,791 --> 00:03:26,375
Before I go, I'd like to
leave you with a parting gift.

34
00:03:26,458 --> 00:03:27,791
A little something

35
00:03:27,875 --> 00:03:30,333
that will help to protect
your broken body.

36
00:03:32,958 --> 00:03:34,333
Within that ring,

37
00:03:34,416 --> 00:03:38,000
I've placed an incredibly
powerful Unrestricted Spell.

38
00:03:38,083 --> 00:03:40,958
However, it will only activate
under certain conditions.

39
00:03:41,041 --> 00:03:41,958
What conditions?

40
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,625
I have one last gift
for you, as well.

41
00:03:47,708 --> 00:03:50,833
I shall name your
Unrestricted Spell,

42
00:03:50,916 --> 00:03:52,791
Grammatica.

43
00:03:52,875 --> 00:03:56,083
Explore the feelings
it brings to mind.

44
00:03:56,166 --> 00:03:57,541
Grammatica?

45
00:04:01,166 --> 00:04:02,750
You're such a silly boy.

46
00:04:09,416 --> 00:04:11,041
We'll we meet again someday.

47
00:04:11,125 --> 00:04:11,958
Till then.

48
00:04:15,166 --> 00:04:16,416
Look, Wilhelmina.

49
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:18,458
I think it'd be best for
the Heir to Both Worlds

50
00:04:18,541 --> 00:04:21,166
to be raised in Xanadu.

51
