you really want!

148
00:10:27,125 --> 00:10:28,333
I'd be glad to.

149
00:10:30,375 --> 00:10:33,125
He's back to the old Yuji.

150
00:10:33,208 --> 00:10:35,833
I want to use the massive
amount of Power of Existence

151
00:10:35,916 --> 00:10:37,291
left behind by
the Denizens

152
00:10:37,375 --> 00:10:39,875
to restore the damage
done to Misaki City.

153
00:10:41,208 --> 00:10:42,416
