154
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:44,041
So that's his plan.

155
00:10:44,125 --> 00:10:46,166
Is that possible?

156
00:10:46,250 --> 00:10:48,041
It is.

157
00:10:48,125 --> 00:10:50,916
You see, Lamies
left me this spell;

158
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:53,416
it's capable of restoring
that which is lost.

159
00:10:55,333 --> 00:10:57,125
Death cannot be undone.

160
00:10:57,208 --> 00:10:58,666
But.

161
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:02,333
