the loss of existence.

162
00:11:02,416 --> 00:11:04,500
The things that we lost,

163
00:11:04,583 --> 00:11:07,791
those the Denizens devoured.

164
00:11:07,875 --> 00:11:11,250
They can be restored with
all this Power of Existence,

165
00:11:11,333 --> 00:11:14,791
my Unrestricted
Spell, and...

166
00:11:14,875 --> 00:11:17,833
The help of Yoshida,
who once tuned Misaki City.

167
00:11:20,666 --> 00:11:22,291
You'll help me, won't you?

168
00:11:26,125 --> 00:11:29,000
He's fast! Is that part
of his Unrestricted Spell?

169
00:11:29,083 --> 00:11:31,458
