completely different now!

170
00:11:31,541 --> 00:11:34,958
Yuji, you plan to restore
your own existence, don't you?

171
00:11:35,041 --> 00:11:37,333
No way, not me.

172
00:11:37,416 --> 00:11:40,791
However, I'd like to
restore Yukari Hirai,

173
00:11:40,875 --> 00:11:42,458
who is a part of you now.

174
00:11:47,541 --> 00:11:49,500
