178
00:12:01,125 --> 00:12:04,750
if she is restored, my mom,
my dad, Ike, Ogata,

179
00:12:04,833 --> 00:12:07,625
and everybody else
will forget you.

180
00:12:07,708 --> 00:12:09,916
But...

181
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:12,416
She would be alive.

182
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,541
Then what happens?

183
00:12:13,625 --> 00:12:17,000
What do you plan
to do after that?

184
00:12:17,083 --> 00:12:18,583
That's all I want.

185
00:12:18,666 --> 00:12:20,666
After that I'll go.

186
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:22,000
Off to Xanadu.

187
00:12:22,083 --> 00:12:24,458
Do you plan to restore
the copy of Misaki City

188
00:12:24,541 --> 00:12:25,708
once you get there?

189
00:12:25,791 --> 00:12:27,750
That's impossible.

190
00:12:27,833 --> 00:12:30,666
Though the new world
is a copy of this one,

191
00:12:30,750 --> 00:12:32,500
there is no Misaki City.

192
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,625
Don't you remember
what I told you before?

193
