If that's the case,

200
00:12:57,791 --> 00:12:59,833
then why're you in such a
hurry to get there, buddy?

201
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:03,958
Transform, Sydonay!

202
00:13:26,958 --> 00:13:28,625
Well, Marcosias.

203
00:13:28,708 --> 00:13:30,500
There's no point in
holdin' back now!

204
00:13:30,583 --> 00:13:33,958
You got that right, my
short fuse, Margery Daw!

205
00:13:46,291 --> 00:13:47,416
Restore it!

206
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,833
Sakai!

207
00:13:48,916 --> 00:13:50,166
Please, Yoshida!

208
00:13:50,250 --> 00:13:51,791
Do this for me!

209
00:13:56,208 --> 00:13:57,625
