I want humans and
Denizens to coexist,

224
00:15:11,166 --> 00:15:13,583
and one rule won't
make that happen!

225
00:15:13,666 --> 00:15:15,666
It isn't an
unrealistic goal.

226
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,041
The Denizens
have shown me

227
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:19,000
this is what they
want, as well.

228
