made the request

233
00:15:34,500 --> 00:15:36,833
to prohibit the
devouring of humans.

234
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,750
I will use the God of
Guidance's oracle

235
00:15:39,833 --> 00:15:41,458
and the Heir to Both Worlds

236
00:15:41,541 --> 00:15:45,583
to ensure they'll never
taste human flesh again!

237
00:15:45,666 --> 00:15:48,000
I don't care how many
centuries it may take me!

238
00:15:48,083 --> 00:15:49,833
In a world
without this city?

239
00:15:49,916 --> 00:15:50,541
That's right!

240
00:15:50,625 --> 00:15:51,666
