00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:23,750
I'm sorry but I
don't have a choice.

262
00:17:23,833 --> 00:17:26,500
After all, I've
taken so many lives.

263
00:17:26,583 --> 00:17:28,708
Flame Haze,
Denizens, Humans.

264
00:17:28,791 --> 00:17:31,541
I knew what I was
doing the entire time.

265
00:17:31,625 --> 00:17:33,875
I want to be with you.

266
00:17:33,958 --> 00:17:36,208
But I was so determined
to change your destiny,

267
00:17:36,291 --> 00:17:37,583
to protect this city,

268
00:17:37,666 --> 00:17:39,833
and protect the
people of this world.

269
00:17:39,916 --> 00:17:41,750
I killed anyone
who got in my way!

270
00:17:41,833 --> 00:17:43,166
That's why!

271
00:17:43,250 --> 00:17:45,666
You've decided wandering
around alone in the new world

272
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,958
is your punishment?

273
00:17:48,041 --> 00:17:50,541
If we were to go there
together I'd be happy,

274
00:17:50,625 --> 00:17:52,416
and then there
would be no point!

275
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:55,375
It's only a punishment
if I lose everything!

276
00:18:09,375 --> 00:18:10,458
Yuji Sakai.

277
00:18:10,541 --> 00:18:12,375
You mustn't blame yourself.

278
00:18:12,458 --> 00:18:14,458
Fine words from the
God of Atonement!

279
00:18:24,750 --> 00:18:26,416
Another Unrestricted Spell?

280
00:18:26,500 --> 00:18:27,375
It's an almighty type!

281
00:18:27,458 --> 00:18:28,500
We can't resist it.

282
00:18:28,583 --> 00:18:29,666
We'll cut through!

283
00:18:38,166 --> 00:18:40,500
Why do you want to
fix everything alone?

284
00:18:40,583 --> 00:18:42,208
I told you.
If I'm not alone,

285
00:18:42,291 --> 00:18:44,208
it isn't a punishment!

286
00:18:44,291 --> 00:18:45,541
But I could help you!

287
00:18:45,625 --> 00:18:47,708
Why can't you get that
through your head!

288
00:18:50,958 --> 00:18:52,500
I would do anything for you

289
00:18:52,583 --> 00:18:55,250
so why won't you agree
to go with me, Yuji?

290
00:18:55,333 --> 00:18:56,875
I can't do that!

291
00:18:58,666 --> 00:19:00,458
Then that's it.

292
00:19:00,541 --> 00:19:02,541
Prepare yourself.

293
00:19:03,541 --> 00:19:07,833
I'll attack you with
everything I have!

294
00:19:18,541 --> 00:19:19,916
Here goes, Marcosias!

295
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:22,250
Let's give him a rhyme
that he won't forget!

296
00:19:22,333 --> 00:19:23,625
I'm all for it!

297
00:19:23,708 --> 00:19:25,750
This is our chance to
take it to the limit!

298
00:19:28,541 --> 00:19:29,583
Who killed cock robin?

299
00:19:29,666 --> 00:19:30,958
I said the sparrow!

300
00:19:31,041 --> 00:19:32,000
Who caught his blood?

301
00:19:32,083 --> 00:19:33,125
I said the fish!

302
00:19:33,208 --> 00:19:34,208
Who'll dig his grave?

303
00:19:34,291 --> 00:19:35,291
I said the owl!

304
00:19:35,375 --> 00:19:36,791
Who'll be chief mourner?

305
00:19:36,875 --> 00:19:38,458
I said the dove!

306
00:19:47,375 --> 00:19:48,708
All of the birds of the air

307
00:19:48,791 --> 00:19:50,833
fell a-sighing and a-sobbing!

308
00:19:59,625 --> 00:20:01,250
Damn it! How much
power is it gonna take

309
00:20:01,333 --> 00:20:02,833
to finally kill
this guy off?

310
00:20:02,916 --> 00:20:04,708
We gotta do this
for all the Flame Haze

311
00:20:04,791 --> 00:20:06,958
this jerk's murdered!

312
00:20:07,041 --> 00:20:09,666
When they heard the bell
toll for poor Cock Robin!

313
00:20:24,708 --> 00:20:26,041
Aw, man!

314
00:20:26,125 --> 00:20:27,458
I'm dyin' here.

315
00:20:29,375 --> 00:20:31,416
Nah, he is.

316
00:20:38,833 --> 00:20:40,083
What happened?

317
00:20:40,166 --> 00:20:42,833
Did you allow them take
your life, General?

318
00:20:42,916 --> 00:20:45,166
Yeah. I did.

319
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:47,416
Deep down I think
that's what I wanted.

320
00:20:49,708 --> 00:20:52,666
I know the three of us
will be together again.

321
00:20:52,750 --> 00:20:54,791
Four, don't forget
about the master.

322
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:59,333
We'll be reunited someday.

323
00:21:03,791 --> 00:21:07,083
It makes perfect sense,
you are underestimating love!

324
00:21:07,166 --> 00:21:09,041
If love is what
inspired your plan,

325
00:21:09,125 --> 00:21:11,291
I think it's okay for you
to be a little selfish.

326
00:21:11,375 --> 00:21:13,166
I forced my will
on everybody.

327
00:21:13,250 --> 00:21:15,250
I can't simply let
go of all that guilt

328
00:21:15,333 --> 00:21:17,208
for the sake of love.

329
00:21:17,291 --> 00:21:18,500
It's all right.

330
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:23,000
I love you anyway.

331
00:21:23,083 --> 00:21:24,833
I love you more
than anyone.

332
00:21:28,958 --> 00:21:30,791
No matter what, if I
think you're in the wrong,

333
00:21:30,875 --> 00:21:32,166
I'll stop you.

334
00:21:32,250 --> 00:21:34,875
If you're suffering,
I'll be there to comfort you.

335
00:21:34,958 --> 00:21:37,208
If you're worried,
I'll talk through it with you.

336
00:21:37,291 --> 00:21:40,000
But you have to promise
you won't ever leave me.

337
00:21:40,083 --> 00:21:41,250
Shana.

338
00:21:41,333 --> 00:21:43,166
I know what you're
thinking, Yuji,

339
00:21:43,250 --> 00:21:45,000
but I wanna know
what you're feeling.

340
00:21:45,083 --> 00:21:46,625
Tell me.

341
00:21:46,708 --> 00:21:51,041
I'm sure I'll do
things that hurt you.

342
00:21:51,125 --> 00:21:53,541
But if I'm suffering
I want you there.

343
00:21:53,625 --> 00:21:55,708
If I'm worried
I'll talk to you

344
00:21:55,791 --> 00:22:00,291
because all I ever
wanted is to be with you.

345
00:22:00,375 --> 00:22:01,583
Same here.

346
00:22:01,666 --> 00:22:02,750
Shana.

347
00:22:25,625 --> 00:22:26,375
What's that?

348
00:22:26,458 --> 00:22:27,500
I dunno.

349
00:22:27,583 --> 00:22:29,541
Lamies gave it to me.

350
00:22:29,625 --> 00:22:32,416
It's an Unrestricted
Spell I'm unfamiliar with.

351
00:22:33,833 --> 00:22:35,791
You're not a Torch anymore.

352
00:22:35,875 --> 00:22:38,208
You're a true existence.

353
00:22:38,291 --> 00:22:39,541
I am?

354
00:22:43,125 --> 00:22:45,833
I never thought I
could be so lucky.

355
00:22:45,916 --> 00:22:49,041
I feel like I
can do anything!

356
00:22:50,708 --> 00:22:53,125
Shall we go to Xanadu,
the new world?

357
00:23:06,416 --> 00:23:09,125
Now Misaki City
is back to normal.

358
00:23:10,583 --> 00:23:13,666
You got what you
wanted, Sakai.

359
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:19,708
[Music]

